        <p class="lead font-serif text-xl">In a world where design trends come and go with increasing speed, creating spaces with enduring elegance requires understanding the fundamental principles that transcend fleeting fashions. This article explores the essential elements of timeless interior design—approaches that have remained relevant through centuries of changing tastes and continue to create spaces that feel both fresh and eternally sophisticated.</p>
        
